├── README.md
└── requirements.txt


## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas & NumPy
- scikit-learn (K-Means, Agglomerative Clustering)
- Matplotlib / Seaborn / Plotly
- Streamlit (optional dashboard)
- GeoPandas / Folium (optional for world maps)

## Installation
1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone <your-repo-url>

Navigate to the project folder:

cd world_development_clustering

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt
Usage

Run clustering scripts:

python models/kmeans_clustering.py
python models/hierarchical_clustering.py

Optional: Run Streamlit app for interactive visualization:

streamlit run app/streamlit_app.py
